&kp PRINTSCREEN xxx             xxx             &kp PG_UP       &kp HOME        &msc SCRL_UP            &mmv MOVE_LEFT  &mmv MOVE_DOWN  &mmv MOVE_UP    &mmv MOVE_RIGHT xxx             &kp C_BRI_UP
